I. Adding the meta-kismet layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-kismet'

Add the following to your local.conf.

'
IMAGE_INSTALL_append = " python3"

CORE_IMAGE_EXTRA_INSTALL += "openssh"
CORE_IMAGE_EXTRA_INSTALL += "python3 gpsd expat gmp imagemagick tiff zlib bzip2 libpcap kismet"
'

